section#clientes
  .container
    .row.justify-content-center
      .col.text-center
        h2(data-l="Clients") Clientes
        p(data-l="Our commitment is to create innovative and profitable programs that generate loyalty and business for our clients.") Nuestro compromiso es crear Programas Innovadores y Rentables que generen Lealtad y Negocio para nuestros Clientes.
    
    .row.justify-content-center.vertical-align.mt-2

      each logo in ['Bbeauty', 'Castrol', 'Cielito Querido Café', 'Cinépolis', 'Citi', 1, 'Costabaja', 'Marina Costabaja', 'Costabaja Resort & Spa', 'Cummins', 'Diablos', 'Eureka', 'Mexalit', 'Elementia', 'Gandhi', 'Georgie Boy', 'Grainger', 'Impulsora', 'Intersygarite', 'Lumen', 1, 'Masisa', 'Melia', 'Samsung', 'Security Finance', 1, 'Grupo ViZion', "Waldo's", 'Eleczion', 'Exprezion']
        if logo==1
          div.jump
        else
          img(src="app/img/clientes/logos-"+slugify(logo)+".png", title=logo alt=logo).clientelogo
    //.row.justify-content-center.vertical-align
      each logo in ["Waldo's", 'Eleczion', 'Exprezion']
        img(src="app/img/clientes/logos-"+slugify(logo)+".png", title=logo alt=logo).clientelogo

  .container.mt-2
    #testimoniosCarr.carousel.slide(data-ride='carousel')
      .carousel-inner
        .carousel-item
          .su-quote.su-quote-style-default.su-quote-has-cite
            .su-quote-inner.su-clearfix
              p(data-l="Blue Pure Loyalty® has proven to be a very professional company, responsible, with leadership of execution and broad knowledge in all what Loyalty is about") Blue Pure Loyalty@ ha demostrado ser un empresa muy profesional, responsable, con liderazgo de ejecuci&oacute;n y amplio expertise en lealtad.
              span.su-quote-cite(data-l="Manuel Muena, Commercial Manager for Masisa Ecuador") Manuel Muena, Gerente Comercial Masisa Ecuador
        .carousel-item
          .su-quote.su-quote-style-default.su-quote-has-cite
            .su-quote-inner.su-clearfix
              p(data-l="Since 2009, Blue Pure Loyalty® has successfully participated in the definition and implementation of various marketing initiatives") Desde 2009 Blue Pure Loyalty@ ha participado exitosamente en la definici&oacute;n e implementaci&oacute;n de las iniciativas de mercadotecnia.
              span.su-quote-cite(data-l="Arturo Peña, General Manager for CostaBaja") Arturo Pe&ntilde;a, Director General CostaBaja
        .carousel-item
          .su-quote.su-quote-style-default.su-quote-has-cite
            .su-quote-inner.su-clearfix
              p(data-l="Blue Pure Loyalty® has proven to be a business partner that shares the commitment, vision and objectives of our company to reach the proposed goals") Blue Pure Loyalty@ ha demostrado ser un socio de negocio que comparte el compromiso, la visi&oacute;n y los objetivos de nuestra empresa para alcanzar las metas propuestas.
              span.su-quote-cite(data-l="Erick Jimenez Muñoz, Club Manager Cinepolis & Cineticket") Erick Jimenez Mu&ntilde;oz, Gerente de Club Cinepolis &amp; Cineticket
        .carousel-item.active
          .su-quote.su-quote-style-default.su-quote-has-cite
            .su-quote-inner.su-clearfix
              p(data-l="With Blue Pure Loyalty® we have worked since 2006 with great success and excellent results") Con Blue Pure Loyalty@ hemos trabajado desde el 2006 con gran &eacute;xito y con excelentes resultados.
              span.su-quote-cite(data-l="Alberto Achar, Marketing Director, Gandhi Bookstores") Alberto Achar, Director de Mercadotecnia Librer&iacute;as Gandhi
      ol.carousel-indicators
        li(data-target='#testimoniosCarr' data-slide-to='0')
        li(data-target='#testimoniosCarr' data-slide-to='1')
        li(data-target='#testimoniosCarr' data-slide-to='2')
        li.active(data-target='#testimoniosCarr' data-slide-to='3')
      a.carousel-control-prev(href='#testimoniosCarr' role='button' data-slide='prev')
        span.carousel-control-prev-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        span.sr-only Anterior
      a.carousel-control-next(href='#testimoniosCarr' role='button' data-slide='next')
        span.carousel-control-next-icon(aria-hidden='true')
        span.sr-only Siguiente
